[[Image:KazenoStigmaAnime.jpg|thumb|250px|The main characters of ''[[Kaze no Stigma]]'']]
This is a '''list of episodes''' of the [[Japan]]ese [[anime|animated]] TV series {{Nihongo|'''''[[Kaze no Stigma]]'''''|<U+98A8><U+306E><U+8056><U+75D5>||lit. ''Stigma of the Wind''}}. The episodes are directed by Jun'ichi Sakata and produced by [[Gonzo (studio)|Gonzo]].<ref name="ANNKazenoStigma">{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/anime.php?id=7473|title=Kaze no Stigma (TV) - Anime News Network|publisher=[[Anime News Network]]|accessdate=2007-11-14}}</ref> They are based on the [[light novel]] series ''Kaze no Stigma'' by Takahiro Yamato, and adapt the source material over twenty-four episodes. The series aired from April 2007 to September 2007 in Japan on [[Chiba TV]], [[KBS Kyoto]], [[Tokyo MX TV]], [[TV Hokkaido]], [[TV Kanagawa]], and [[TV Saitama]].<ref name="ANNKazenoStigma"/>

Four pieces of [[theme music]] are used for the episodes; one opening theme and three ending themes. The opening theme is "blast of wind" by Saori Kiuji. The ending themes are Kiuju's "Hitori Kiri no Sora" and "Matataki no Kiwoku" by [[Ayumi Fujimura]], [[Yuka Inokuchi]] and [[Shizuka It<U+014D>]], with either played for all episodes save episode twelve, which features Sakai Tanako's "Tsuki Hana no Inori."

One DVD compilation was released by Gonzo on [[August 24]], [[2007]].<ref name="DVDStuff">{{cite web|url=http://pc.webnt.jp/stigma/007cddvd/#a000040|title=<U+98A8><U+306E><U+30B9><U+30C6><U+30A3><U+30B0><U+30DE><U+3000><U+516C><U+5F0F><U+30B5><U+30A4><U+30C8>: CD<U+30FB>DVD<U+30FB><U+66F8><U+7C4D>|accessdate=2007-11-14}}</ref>

