 |JapaneseTitle=Kako to no Taiketsu
 |KanjiTitle=<U+904E><U+53BB><U+3068><U+306E><U+5BFE><U+6C7A>
 |EnglishTitle=Facing the Past
 |OriginalAirDate=[[April 18]] [[2007]]
 |ShortSummary=Kazuma's father, [[Kaze no Stigma#Kannagi family|Gemna Kannagi]] tries to bring him back to the Kannagi family's main house to answer some questions, but Kazuma wants to fight him instead. He ends up defeating his father with a special wind technique. Later, he meets his brother, [[Kaze no Stigma#Kannagi family|Ren Kannagi]] again after four years, but the powerful wind user from before kidnaps his brother. Kazuma vows to bring him back.
}}
